examples.en: Proper attire is required at the restaurant.
Waiters in tropical attire are part of the restaurant's shtick.
The restaurant considers jeans and T-shirts incorrect attire for dinner.
She needed some snazzy attire for the job interview.
He was surrounded by a bevy of beauties in bathing attire.
